Here is another way to create the pidfile (or any file, for that matter):

int create(char *path)
{
     int fd;

     if((fd=open(path, CREATE|EXCL|WRONLY, READ|WRITE)) == -1)
     {
          return(0);
     }
     close(fd);
     return(1);
}

Note that create() returns a 1 on success and a 0 on failure.

